replyTime":"2017-08-31T16:20:03.000Z","msg":"明知自己一句起 兩句止 仲要nature 仲要一路答 一路諗 除非中我鐘意既topic 就可以係咁吹水"},{"pid":"1c46c6672002cf1dd9b794c0bf38594497540f79","tid":382374,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T16:50:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全唔會知下一秒會係出咩問題 玩死我 就算明佢問乜都唔可以變到吹水咁 咁多野講</blockquote><br />\n其實表現愈輕鬆 愈<span style=\"color: red;\">natural</span> 愈加分 唔好答得太死</blockquote><br />\n屌打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f58f7a1afbfbef3e5206ae0322d9767ce97adfdf","tid":382374,"uid":37688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T17:06:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明知自己一句起 兩句止 仲要nature 仲要一路答 一路諗 除非中我鐘意既topic 就可以係咁吹水</blockquote><br />\n盡量諗有乜就放開d講出黎 你當同佢傾計 討論佢問既議題咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我考果陣個問題都唔係好諗到 唯有盡吹<br />\n最後6.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e071cb4b1435f32e560d52b8813a7240e07ad74f","tid":382374,"uid":81756,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T17:29:44.000Z","msg":"speakimg係外國考/考官係鬼個分會靚d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d3f74950f66f3b7d07864f01a240751ac7d53c","tid":382374,"uid":139937,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T20:00:58.000Z","msg":"Speaking要唔停嘴咁不停講<br />\n最緊要唔好怯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得考之前望吓有咩題目考嗰陣會比較有信心<br />\n有個強國網頁叫「雅思哥」有人整理咗呢一排嘅題目<br />\n唔介意殘體字可以望吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其他果啲咪操吓卷知道考試形式應該完全夠<br />\n尤其reading listening 普通香港學生應該祼考都起碼考到7.5啦<br />\nIELTS嘅Pastpaper普通書局都有賣 不過好L貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20e27bf092fa751631ce26b770ae663aa37637e","tid":382374,"uid":91732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T23:31:42.000Z","msg":"怯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  勁怯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d96ca47688be46a509dc663477a39a5d78118058","tid":382374,"uid":106958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T00:14:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a97bf50f450160ddc3ed85b81a785277e9501c8","tid":382374,"uid":16041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T00:19:04.000Z","msg":"Speaking會翻炒"},{"pid":"a6342dd7ed8ac38be8284ad40cccff799cda4aff","tid":382374,"uid":17479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T00:33:20.000Z","msg":"我覺得speaking有時係考反應多過考英文<br />\n之前佢問我搵一樣植物代表自己國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> on99<br />\n<br />\nReading Listening 做多聽多一定有7<br />\n<br />\n反而writing真係最難 要做到精而簡 用詞恰當 文法暢順  好撚難 <br />\n<br />\n利申：8 8 8 6.5<br />\n<br />\n衰writing:/<br />\n<br />\n但有時marginally missed offer 學校都會收 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35fd718afde571d3ff6f45090e4f0618265f8069","tid":382374,"uid":110892,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T01:58:54.000Z","msg":"IELTS speaking 都唔係考英文, 考吹水"},{"pid":"32ab3df238c27914c85cb6b10d6a435538eefc42","tid":382374,"uid":139937,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T04:30:09.000Z","msg":"補充一下 我今年六月初考 分數係9 8.5 7 7.5 <br />\n我記得我嗰陣speaking係每一題講到考官嗌停我為止<br />\n其實speaking 冇啲人講到咁恐佈 我嗰時仲係傳說中俾分最strict 嘅Asian閪面女考官𠻹<br />\n考完dse嗰陣考 以為自己英文好掂<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">最後dse英文攞5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"61fa1273c0e041f1ded8c06cd7933944fce65fbb","tid":382374,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201